Q1) Your team reports that an application running in kubernetes has become slow and users are experiencing high reposnse times.How 
  would you solve this problem?
ans-> 1. Check pod utitlization. Increase resources if they are under limit

  Kubectl get pods --sort-by=cpu
  Kubectl ger pods --sort-by=memory

 Q2)Describe the slow pod to show more information.Look for resource throttling.restart count,or liveness probe failures.
  
